node.text:
Soft, cozy, and super comfortable, the Ergobaby Embrace carrier is the sweetest way to stay connected. No complicated wrapping or tying! The Embrace keeps you and baby close as you find your new rhythm together. 

*Note: Our baby doll measures a little bit below the recommended height for two of these positions—we illustrate the positions for demonstrative purposes.

node.text: Take a look at two of our favorite swaddle brands: Copper Pearl and Love to Dream! Copper Pearl swaddles are made of the softest, stretchiest fabric and can double as a cozy blanket.
